rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0001
rows.name: So...where do we go from here?

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, there's no point heading back,
so I guess we just press on?

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0003
rows.name:
I guess so...
Forward is the only way.

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0004
rows.name:
We'll just have to head over that
fallen building.

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0005
rows.name:
We may have him with us, but he's not
in the best shape, and we have fewer
fighters around than we're used to.

rows.label: fev08_090_150_msg0006
rows.name:
We should exercise caution
as we proceed.
